---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About VaultMill">
  <section class="page">
    <h1>About VaultMill</h1>

    <p>
      VaultMill is an independent platform dedicated to publishing
      factual, well-organized profiles of influential business
      leaders. Our goal is to make it easier to learn about the
      executives who shape industries, lead global organizations,
      and influence the direction of business and technology.
    </p>

    <p>
      Each profile is designed to bring together key information in
      a consistent format, including career history, leadership
      roles, education, board memberships, and other publicly
      available information. As the platform grows, additional
      relationships between executives, companies, industries, and
      organizations will provide broader context and make discovery
      easier.
    </p>

    <p>
      VaultMill emphasizes accuracy, clarity, and maintainability.
      Every profile is built from structured content, allowing the
      platform to grow while remaining consistent and easy to update.
      This approach supports a continually expanding library of
      executive profiles without sacrificing quality or usability.
    </p>

    <p>
      Today, VaultMill is focused on executive biographies. Over
      time, it will evolve into a broader knowledge resource that
      connects leaders, organizations, and the milestones that have
      shaped modern business.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>